<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Session Reminder – Graphora</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f0f0f;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 26px;
        }

        .header p {
            margin: 8px 0 0;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 36px 32px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .countdown {
            text-align: center;
            background: #242424;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .countdown .time {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #f59e0b;
        }

        .countdown .label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .detail-card {
            background: #242424;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        }

        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #2e2e2e;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .detail-label {
            color: #888;
        }

        .detail-value {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .btn {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 24px auto;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #d97706);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .checklist {
            background: #1e2a1e;
            border: 1px solid #2d4a2d;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .checklist p {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            color: #86efac;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .checklist ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #a0c4a0;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .checklist li {
            margin: 4px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #111;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
            border-top: 1px solid #222;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #6366f1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>⏰ Session Starting Soon!</h1>
            <p>Your mentorship session is about to begin</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{recipientName}},</h2>
            <p>This is a reminder that your session with <strong>{{mentorName}}</strong> is starting soon.</p>

            <div class="countdown">
                <div class="time">{{minutesUntil}} min</div>
                <div class="label">until your session starts</div>
            </div>

            <div class="detail-card">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Mentor</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{mentorName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Scheduled At</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{scheduledAt}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Booking ID</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{bookingId}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="checklist">
                <p>✅ Pre-session checklist:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Test your microphone and camera</li>
                    <li>Find a quiet, well-lit space</li>
                    <li>Have your questions ready</li>
                    <li>Open the meeting link below</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <a href="{{meetingLink}}" class="btn">🎥 Join Session Now</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>© 2025 Graphora. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>